Makes sure you do RASA on ubuntu. It is very important because RASA X is well supported in ubuntu.
RASA X is advanced version of the RASA chatbot development.

Steps to follow:
Step1:
open terminal and update the setting 
install pip and python
install vitualenv

Step2:
creating a virtualenv
command
1: virtualenv virtualenv_name

2: virtualenv -p /usr/bin/python3 virtualenv_name

3: source virtualenv_name/bin/activate

4: cd virtualenv_name

5: pip install rasa

6: rasa init

7: rasa x

Click on this below link for more detail:
https://rasa.com/docs/rasa/user-guide/installation/

